                Eurocode 8 Seismic Design Calculator (Response Spectrum & Base
                Shear)
              </h1>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Compute elastic and design response spectra, design ground
                acceleration, behaviour factor and base shear according to EN
                1998‑1 (Eurocode 8) for buildings.
