                <span class="badge bg-purple-100 text-purple-800"
                  >Base shear</span
                >
              </div>
              <p
                class="mt-3 text-xs text-amber-700 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded px-3 py-2"
              >
                This tool is for educational and preliminary design use only.
                Always verify with the full text of Eurocode 8, the relevant
                National Annex and professional engineering judgement.
              </p>
            </header>

            <!-- Calculator UI -->
            <section aria-labelledby="calculator-heading">
              <h2 id="calculator-heading" class="sr-only">
                Eurocode 8 seismic design calculator
